            "block_description": "Everything you need to know about lab grown diamonds.",
            "faq_question_1": "What are lab grown diamonds?",
            "faq_answer_1": "<p>Lab grown diamonds are real diamonds created in controlled laboratory environments. They have the same physical, chemical, and optical properties as natural diamonds, offering identical brilliance and durability.</p>",
            "faq_question_2": "Are lab grown diamonds real diamonds?",
            "faq_answer_2": "<p>Yes. Lab grown diamonds are 100% real diamonds. They are not simulants like cubic zirconia or moissanite. The only difference is their origin, not their composition or appearance.</p>",
            "faq_question_3": "How are lab grown diamonds different from natural diamonds?",
            "faq_answer_3": "<p>The main difference is how they are formed. Natural diamonds form over billions of years underground, while lab grown diamonds are created using advanced technology. Visually and structurally, they are the same.</p>",
            "faq_question_4": "Are lab grown diamonds certified?",
            "faq_answer_4": "<p>Yes. Lab grown diamonds are certified by internationally recognised gemological institutes such as IGI and SGL. Certification ensures quality, authenticity, and transparency in grading.</p>",
            "faq_question_5": "Why are lab grown diamonds more affordable?",
            "faq_answer_5": "<p>Lab grown diamonds cost less because they are produced in controlled environments with efficient processes. This makes them a smarter choice for larger, high-quality diamonds without compromising on beauty or performance.</p>",
